Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.55,0:00:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Always keep your pokerface...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.26,0:00:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking my father's teaching to my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The miracle magician glides amidst the skycraper.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief, prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Akako?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's target is Kaito's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:02:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas Eve on The Slopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic of the Underworld…..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who rule the darkness…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me power…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me power…!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I cast red magic on these matching patches…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever I stick them on will instantly fall in love,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and be bound together as partners…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito Kuroba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make you mine, once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a nice day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And we get to have ski lessons on Christmas, it's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, it's too perfect!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can just see it now, the ski slopes under the stars…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh…um…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think our teacher's more excited than we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone looks so happy…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know how to ski at all…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,…Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mixed hot springs, boys and girls together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so carefree…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He has no idea he's going to be all mine soon…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Akako!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, ski with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Akako, with me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.90,0:03:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys, back in your seats!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhhhhh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Uwaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Noooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, cut that out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been bumping into me this whole time!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm doing it on purpose…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so bad at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help it! I'm a beginner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Another marital dispute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo, whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ski over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you stop going wherever I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they doing…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But that Aoko Nakamori…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What an obnoxious girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I try to get near him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always by his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, everyone, gather around!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So! Today we have organized a special event for the evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A special event?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard about this…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you haven't heard about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just telling you about it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the "Christmas Eve Costume Ski Party."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, choose a partner and ski as a couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaaat!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For real!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we be in girl-girl pairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be a boy and girl couple…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Two sets of trails left on the slopes at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A world where only the two of you exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It will certainly be an unforgettable page of your youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4}"beautiful"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Our teacher's got stars in her eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness, what a wonderful idea I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Th…that is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, choose your partners!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There are costumes in the lodge,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,choose and create your own looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a prize for the winning couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Get…a partner…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The other class is having a snowboarding competition
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never going to be partners with a bad skier like you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoko, can I talk to you for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Akako.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoko…you like Kaito, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, n-n-n-not at all!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito isn't the simple boy you think he is…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What…do you mean by that…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's more complex…more mysterious…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mysterious…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, he's not compatible with an ordinary girl like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to make a wager with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,As to who can pair up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lose, you have to give him up right away…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh…why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's funny!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That a beautiful girl like you likes Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know Kaito was that popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Um! You really are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell me, what do you even like about Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What, I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the wager's on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you, blushing…Akako's so cute…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see…I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ack!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,…I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh…uh, oh
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujie!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Akakooooo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Akako!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Akako…so you like Akako, Fujie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it will never be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll never like a guy like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody notices me, I'm fat, I can't ski…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought today I'd have the courage and…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,today would be the day…but…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no girl in the world who would pay attention to me…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.65,0:08:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not, that's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,…Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to ski with me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We both can't ski, so we'll help each other…and do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,B…but you've got Kaito…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no…Kaito's got Aka…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to ski with someone good at skiing, I'm sure…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Woohoo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo! Kaito sure is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,See you ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Byeeee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:09:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a good skier, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, Akako…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl's kind of strange…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Again!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoko. You just never get better, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito and Akako…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever! I'm doing my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Go over there and build a snowman or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujie…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, you haven't chosen yours yet have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, your partner for this evening's something or other...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, alright, I'll be your partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaat!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.11,0:09:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh…I promised Fujie that I'd be his partner…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, with Fujie….what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I did
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujie said…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:09:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:09:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What a perfect match for you, Aoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, let's go, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,See you, enjoy making snowmen together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You're so nervous…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not nervous…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hee hee…how cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be my partner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! I'm so cute in this outfit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, whatever…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, the view is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, whatever…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the spell even working on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he that insensitive…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're completely up in space!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the great Kid the Phantom Thief is nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,when it comes to that girl, is that it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I…I have no idea what you're talking about…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing you the favor of offering myself to you…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I could make you my partner for life, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A…alright…alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to be your partner, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh look at you, you're blushing…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be working after all, my magic patches…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,those wearing the patches fall in love, and will be partners…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good at dealing with this woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm bored, I'm so bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The baths are mixed boys and girls, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There was nobody in there when I looked before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Aoko
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch…my whole body hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoko? Oh no…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look. There's someone over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaat!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cute, husky voice!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a girl…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Aoko, why didn't you partner with Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why didn't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because…I'm a bad skier…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What, so that's why you decided not to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito's a good skier so I'd just embarrass myself if I skied with him…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Kaito was your personal coach…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.87,0:13:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, why didn't he ask you to be your partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so immature!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, thanks for the advice…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But, that's also a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He lost his father when he was young…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know all about it…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He…loved him so much…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But he never looked sad or lonely,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,he just goofs around like he always does, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, as an old friend…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I want him to, you know, look cool when he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's fine like this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fine!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eww!! This is awful!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Toh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit still will you!!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, what does she mean, it's fine like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,…Is it really…fine like this…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,…Is it really, fine like this…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Miss Akako"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief is here…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Aoko tell you you'll win if you dress as \NKid and Inspector Nakamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I think your stomach's even bigger than it usually is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Th…this…is for Ms. Akako…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too scared to give it to her…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Aoko encouraged me…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So…so…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoko wants to ski with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,… Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a present for you, Fujie
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh…what is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, things are about to get a little busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, everyone!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for the Christmas Eve Costume Ski Party to begin!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd Fujie go…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, entry number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pandas Ling-Ling and Shing-Shing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Y…yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Vampire and werewolf!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor and nurse!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Octopus and bird!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinosaur and bug!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Masked Yaiber and Monster!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Aoko…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I win the wager…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Entry number eighteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Snow Queen and Yeti!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Kaito
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Feast your eyes on our beautiful skiing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ack!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,F…Fujie!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ms. Akako…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,…Why…he looks to me so,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,different from before…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Akako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He looks dazzling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,M-m-m-merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:18:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Fujie! Now, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Akako Koizumi! Leading beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Demonstrating brilliant pair skiing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful, Ms. Akako!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Akako, why won't you ski with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty-nine points!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the top score, Fujie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ms. Akako!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened to Aoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito hasn't skied yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Akako!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he doing…the sun's about to go down…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dark to see anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask me to be your partner sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ka…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:19:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito, you idioooooooot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I am an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,K…Kaito…is that you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujie's skied already with his love, Ms. Akako.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito…you look like the real Kid…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? I look better than the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we've got to do something about your costume…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,At least...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to go at least this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you touch my bum just now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Last entry, Kid the Phantom Thief and Queen Nakamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,B…but…I can't ski…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not scared of falling anymore, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So relax, tell yourself you can ski, and you'll ski.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,…Alright! …
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kaito! Kaito's magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dressing up as Kid the Phantom Thief…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bold boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A perfect score!! Kaito Kuroba and Aoko Nakamori!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You got me…Kaito Kuroba…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've fallen under my own spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But that means my magic worked, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are so clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What, oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never catch me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.91,0:21:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid the Phantom Thief, I'll get you this time!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh…what is this…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.71,0:22:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a hand made figurine of you, Ms. Akako!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.08,0:22:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Akako!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas! Ms. Akako!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept my present!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.91,0:22:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Akako!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Akako!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.46,0:22:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Akako!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.54,0:22:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I'm Kaito Kuroba!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.21,0:24:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while. How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.87,0:24:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'll be seeing you every week this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.83,0:24:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They say they're going to show me getting arrested
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.62,0:24:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,on live TV next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.87,0:24:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That Inspector Nakamori never gives up…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.12,0:24:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.04,0:24:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a great detective back from London,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.79,0:24:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and a world famous illusionist after me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.37,0:24:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tough being so popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.37,0:24:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on "Magic Kaito,"\N"The Gorgeous Rivals"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.71,0:24:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you under the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.83,0:24:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Kid's magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.17,0:24:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"White Horse (Hakuba)"
